Personalized Home Care Services
If you are looking for home care assistance services, Homewatch Caregivers is here to help you. We give your elderly parents the quality home care they deserve. With 12 years of experience, we have been offering customized senior care, prenatal and post-natal care, travel care services and more.

We have a team of trained and educated caregivers. We proudly serve Santa Clara and the surrounding area. We take pride in our excellent treatment options and quality nursing care in a safe environment. To learn more about our services, call us at (408) 714-0127.

Our Services Include:

Senior Care
Care for Chronic Conditions and Degenerative Disorders
After Surgery Care
Home Health Care Services
At-Home Physical Therapies
Pain and Prescription Management
Personal Care and Companion Services
Medication Reminders







