Addus HomeCare, Inc.

















888.233.8746
info1@addus.com






























Dual Advantage
Effective integration of in-home personal care and medical services drives better medical outcomes and lowers costs, while improving quality of life.
Learn more about Dual AdvantageClick Here





Veterans
We ensure veterans customized and easy access to supportive services they need as they age. In partnership with Veterans Care Coordination (VCC), we give veterans the ability to select benefits based on their eligibility.
Learn more about our veteran care servicesClick Here





Caregivers
Our professional Care Team currently provides a full range of home care services to more than 30,000 clients. Every day, Addus caregivers create peace of mind for our clients and their families.
Learn more about becoming a caregiverClick Here





Clients & Family
Our individualized treatment plans focus on consistent, effective care and patient education, leading to improved client health outcomes, quality of life and peace of mind.
Learn more about client and family servicesClick Here










Addus ... The Pre-Acute Solution to the Post-Acute Problem. SM

Since 1979, Addus has served families at home, providing quality in-home supportive services to elderly and younger persons with disabilities. Our approach is simple: We provide great care and we pay attention. In the conduct of providing our services, we watch for important changes in health condition so we can promptly get that information to the appropriate health resource.Early identification leads to early intervention. Early intervention leads to lower health care costs and a dramatic increase in quality of life for our consumers. That is our purpose and 
					how we should be measured.

Explore ServicesBecome a Caregiver

















