Welcome to Our Career Center!




Join Our Team

At Addus, we value our employees. They are our greatest asset and the reason for our success. They love what they do and are personally fulfilled by their work and the impact they have on the clients, families and communities that we serve.
There’s no better time to join Addus!

It’s an exciting time in the healthcare industry and Addus is a company on the move. We are a client-focused, innovative and forward-thinking company and we are always looking for top talent. We are building a dynamic team of dedicated individuals seeking meaningful employment in a supportive and rewarding environment.
If you share a genuine passion for serving others and want to work for a values-driven organization that recognizes and appreciates your contributions, we encourage you to read about our company and review our job opportunities to see if there is a match for your skills, experience and interests.

