Investors considering a purchase of Addus HomeCare Corp shares, but cautious about paying the going market price of $36.08/share, might benefit from considering selling puts among the alternative strategies at their disposal. One interesting put contract in particular, is the July put at the $30 strike, which has a bid at the time of this writing of $1.55.

